⚖️ The key difference (this is important)

There are two modes:

❌ Closed loop (dangerous)

* Believe → filter reality to match → reinforce belief
* No real testing
* Leads to distortion / overconfidence

✅ Open loop (what you’re describing)

* Believe → test → allow contradiction → update
* Reality has veto power

That second one is how you actually get stronger over time.

